%N A167599 Number of reduced words of length n in Coxeter group on 42 generators S_i with relations (S_i)^2 = (S_i S_j)^14 = I.
%C A167599 The initial terms coincide with those of A170761, although the two sequences are eventually different.
%C A167599 Computed with Magma using commands similar to those used to compute A154638.
